title: compareNoCase
name: compareNoCase
description:
Performs a case-insensitive comparison of two strings.
        An indicator of the difference:
            A negative number, if string1 is less than string2
            0, if string1 is equal to string2
            A positive number, if string1 is greater than string2

arguments.name: string1
arguments.description: A string or a variable that contains one

arguments.name: string2
arguments.description: A string or a variable that contains one
